long_description:
Benessere, identità, successo
Non importa quale sia la tua impresa, la nostra missione è garantirle un ambiente accogliente e funzionale. Ci occupiamo di arredamento per uffici in Toscana e non solo. Creiamo soluzioni per ambienti di lavoro capaci di aumentare il benessere e la produttività dei lavoratori e delle lavoratrici; capaci di raccontare l'identità del brand e di dare il giusto spazio alla crescita e al successo dell'impresa che li vive. Personalizzazione, qualità, vicinanza
Perseguiamo la nostra missione attraverso servizi integrati e personalizzati; con prodotti e marchi di qualità, capaci di rispondere in maniera puntuale alle molteplici e specifiche esigenze di ogni singola impresa. E attraverso un approccio orientato alla vicinanza al cliente in tutte le fasi di lavoro: dalla consulenza iniziale alla preventivazione, dalla fase di ordinazione e rapporto con la casa di produzione alla consegna e montaggio, fino all'assistenza post vendita. La presenza sul territorio toscano è garantita dalla sede ARREDOTEAM di Firenze e da quella di Livorno, dove abbiamo anche uno showroom di 400 mq e un magazzino per i mobili ufficio pronta consegna. Tuttavia per vicinanza non intendiamo solo una presenza territoriale ma soprattutto un modo di curare la relazione con tutti i clienti, in termini di presenza costante e personalizzata. Pur contando su diverse figure, commerciali, consulenti, progettisti, ogni progetto ARREDOTEAM è affidato a un unico referente che si interfaccia con il cliente, segue, consiglia, sollecita, presenzia e risolve problemi in ogni momento, dal primo contatto alla consegna dell'ambiente che abbiamo progettato insieme.

short_description: CALZATURIFICIO SOLDINI is a shoes & other footwear store based in San Martino Soprarno, Italy.
long_description: La storia del Calzutirificio Soldini inizia nel lontano 1945 a Capolona, un piccolo paese in provincia di Arezzo, dove ancora oggi si trova il cuore dell'azienda. Gustavo Soldini, insieme ai fratelli Giuseppe ed Ermenegildo subentrano alla morte del padre nel laboratorio di calzature con la societ\u00e0 denominata "Fratelli Soldini", avviando un'attivit\u00e0 prettamente artigianale di realizzazione di calzature per uomo e donna rivolte al mercato locale di Arezzo e Firenze. Negli anni 50' con lo sviluppo dell'attivit\u00e0 viene aperto un primo stabilimento a Capolona, sulle rive del fiume Arno, e successivamente un secondo ad Anghiari segnando il passaggio da produzione artigianale a quella industriale ed arrivando ad impiegare pi\u00f9 di 800 dipendenti. Per far fronte alla recessione economica dell'Italia e alla crisi del settore calzaturiero derivante anche dalla crescita dei paesi emergenti, negli anni 80′ l'azienda decide di puntare sull'internazionalizzazione e sulla diversificazione di prodotto.

generated_description: Soldini is a footwear company based in San Martino Soprarno, Tuscany. Founded in 1945 by Gustavo Soldini and his brothers Giuseppe and Ermenegildo, the company initially operated as an artisanal business producing footwear for men and women in the local Arezzo and Florence markets. Over the years, Soldini expanded its production capabilities and market reach, transitioning from artisanal to industrial manufacturing and employing over 800 people. In the 1980s, the company focused on internationalization and product diversification, launching new brands such as Stone Haven and Soldini Sport, and expanding its product line to include civil, professional, and military footwear under the Soldini Professional brand. In 2018, Soldini introduced the Antica Cuoieria brand, which combines traditional craftsmanship with modern technology. The company is known for its commitment to Italian manufacturing excellence, quality materials, and innovative designs.

short_description: CLAGS The Center for LGBTQ Studies is a college/university based in York, Nebraska, United States.
long_description: CLAGS: The Center for LGBTQ Studies (formerly known as Center for Lesbian and Gay Studies or CLAGS) was founded in 1991 by professor Martin Duberman as the first university-based research center in the United States dedicated to the study of historical, cultural, and political issues of lesbian, gay, bisexual, and transgender (LGBT) individuals and communities. Housed at the Graduate Center, CUNY, CLAGS sponsors public programs and conferences, offers fellowships to individual scholars, and functions as a conduit of information. It also serves as a national center for the promotion of scholarship that fosters social change. The center is located at the Graduate Center of the City University of New York, 365 Fifth Avenue, in New York City. Past executive directors include Martin Duberman, Alissa Solomon, Jill Dolan, Paisley Currah, Sarah Chinn, James Wilson, and Kevin Nadal. Nadal was the first person of color to hold the executive director role. The current executive director is Justin Brown.

short_description: Fireweed Community Market is a fruit & vegetable market based in Whitehorse, Yukon, Canada.
long_description: We celebrate Yukon culture at our markets 'where local happens'. Our mandate "The Fireweed Community Market Society is an enduring cooperative community of people who wish to promote diverse and conscientious local production and consumption.". The Fireweed Community Market Society has been operating in Whitehorse since 2005 on the land of Ta'an Kwäch'än Council and Kwanlin Dün First Nation. We promote the production and consumption of Yukon products. We offer authentic experiences to residents and tourists by supporting local entrepreneurs and small businesses and directly connecting consumers with producers of quality goods that are locally grown, raised, wild-harvested, or hand-crafted -the Fireweed Community Market Society in Whitehorse. Since 2005, a volunteer board has guided the strategic and operational success of our non-profit society, with the support of part-time and seasonal staff, over 250 members and hundreds of volunteer hours. Long term funding from the Canadian Agricultural Partnership program provides significant support.

short_description: Jbay Recycling Project is a garbage collection & waste disposal services company based in Jeffreys Bay, South Africa.
long_description: We are The JBay Recycling Project and we've been turning trash in to treasure for 10 years. Our concept is simple: encourage children to keep their streets clean and reward them with things they really need. The Project is exclusively for children and is run predominantly with the help of volunteers. We do hire a handful of casual laborers to assist us on site, thereby also giving back to the community within which we operate. Our three main objectives are to clean up the environment, help alleviate poverty and to educate as well as nurture. We are aware of the impact we have and that is one of the reasons we simply can't stop. If what we do resonates with you please consider getting involved, we operate every Monday during school terms from 12pm until 4pm. Your financial contributions are also vital to our continuation as many of the products in our shop are purchased when donations are not available.

short_description: Kwara State Polytechnic Ilorin is a college/university based in Ilorin, Nigeria.
long_description:
Our Vision
To be the foremost provider of Technological and Entrepreneurial skills. Our Mission
To teach, impart and foster the highest level of intellectual development and provide services to humanity through the exploration of available scientific and research methods. History Of Kwara State Polytechnic
The Kwara State Polytechnic, Ilorin was established by his Excellency, the then Military Governor of Kwara State, Col. David Bamigboye. The decision to establish the Polytechnic was announced during the launching of the four Year Development plan in 1971.The College eventually came into existence following the promulgation of Kwara State Edict no. 4 of 1972 (now overtaken by the edict no. 21 of 1984 edict No. 13 of 1987 and edict no. 7 of 1994) as a body empowered by statute "to provide for studies, training, research and development of techniques in arts and language, applied sciences, engineering, management and commerce, education and well as in other spheres of learning".The Kwara State Polytechnic formally commenced operation in January 1973 with an administrative machinery patterned closely after the existing universities in the country. The polytechnic has as its motto: TECHNOLOGY, INNOVATION AND SERVICE.At its inception in 1973, the Polytechnic had 110 students, 11 members of academic staff and 3 senior administrative staff.

Since it was first established in the year 1991, the group of ambitious founders have led the way forward for the then modest company to become one of the largest and most reputable First-Grade general contracting companies in Jordan. Reliability, credibility, and implementation of international best practices have always paved the way forward for MID Contracting and its team. Today, MID Contracting Company Ltd. occupies a distinct position in the construction contracting industry of Jordan and the MENA region, with a unique portfolio and track record of specialized projects in roads, infrastructure networks, leisure, hospitals and healthcare facilities, industrial, marine, and telecommunications, with a global network of international partners, alliances, and suppliers
MID Contracting is a limited liability company comprising of Jordanian and International partners, and is classified by the Jordanian Ministry of Public Works and Housing as Grade "A" General Contracting Company, with First Grade classification in the following specializations:• Buildings Construction• Electromechanics and Renewable Energy• Roads Construction• Earth Works / Excavation and Excavation for Mining• Water and Sewerage• Concrete Works/ Bridges & Intersections & Tunnels• Communication Networks• Decor Works and Furnishing MID contracting was the first Jordanian contracting company to acquire the ISO 9001 certification. Our headquarters is located in the Zhangjiang Hi-Tech Parkin the China (Shanghai) Pilot Free Trade Zone and it has an industrial base covering 66,600m². The world-wide commercial ultracapacitor electric city bus line was opened in Shanghai in 2006, namely Shanghai Line 11. Men dette skal gjøres innenfor det vi er gode på, nemlig og tilby våre kunder og samarbeidspartnere de beste produktene, de beste løsningene til konkurransedyktige priser slik at resultatet er de mest fornøyde kundene. Vi bestemte oss våren 2010 for en kontrollert avvikling av vårt entreprenør selskap etter 25 år og videreføre vår kompetanse inn i et nytt selskap som fikk navnet Byggmesterkontoret. Sistnevnte selskap ble opprettet i 2009 og vi har hatt en klar profil om og tilby produkter og løsninger av høy kvalitet innen fagområdet inneklima. Vi inngikk tidlig i 2010 import avtaler med produsenter av produkter innenfor fagområdet inneklima og vår virksomhet er to delt i form av vårt ansvar som importør med videresalg til forhandlere samt egen salgs og innstallatør avdeling som tilbyr produkter, løsninger og innstallering til privatkunder.

short_description: CEFAREA-ARIAS is a legal association based in Paris, France.
long_description: CEFAREA-ARIAS a pour mission principale de promouvoir les modes alternatifs de règlement des conflits, plus particulièrement la médiation et l'arbitrage dans les litiges pouvant opposer des acteurs du monde de l'assurance dans son ensemble et sa diversité. Le recours à l'arbitrage est une tradition ancienne dans les relations entre les assureurs et les réassureurs. Les avantages sont bien connus : Rapidité, Confidentialité et professionnalisme des « Juges ».Fort de sa longue expérience et de sa connaissance de l'évolution du milieu professionnel, CEFAREA-ARIAS propose aujourd'hui des solutions rapides, efficaces et professionnelles adaptées aux besoins de chacun. Les principales procédures utilisées sont la médiation et l'arbitrage. Il s'adresse à tous les acteurs, assureurs, réassureurs, mutuelles, institutions de prévoyance, intermédiaires grossistes, spécialistes, de proximité, aux conseils en gestion de patrimoines, gestionnaires, etc. Le recours à un centre organisé est une nécessité. Celui-ci sélectionne des arbitres et des médiateurs formés et reconnus. Il dispose de règlements clairs et précis évitant aux parties d'avoir à prévoir par elles-même toutes les modalités de gestion de leur conflit. En matière d'arbitrage, une commission de professionnels de haut niveau permet au centre d'exercer une fonction quasi juridictionnelle permettant de résoudre différentes difficultés sans être contraints de recourir au juge professionnel (juge d'appui). Bien entendu, le recours à CEFAREA-ARIAS permet en outre de s'adresser à une organisation professionnelle reconnue, dont les membres connaissent parfaitement la typologie des litiges, leurs difficultés et enjeux. CEFAREA-ARIAS est à la disposition de la profession.

long_description: La Feria de Teatro en el Sur de Palma del Río (Córdoba) es una iniciativa municipal que nace en 1984 con el objetivo de mostrar, promocionar y difundir las creaciones del amplio sector del teatro y la danza de Andalucía. Concebida en principio como una "Muestra de teatro andaluz", en el año 1992 el modelo de organización evoluciona hasta convertirse en "Feria de Teatro", priorizando y dinamizando el papel de mercado de la escena andaluza/foro de negocio. Por antigüedad, se trata de la segunda iniciativa de estas características que existe en el territorio español (la Feria de Tárrega surge en el año 1981) y la única que existe en Andalucía. A través de un proyecto colectivo, con continuidad, en permanente crecimiento y en cooperación con los agentes implicados, la Feria de Teatro en el Sur de Palma del Río pretende ser una herramienta de utilidad para la consolidación del sector de las artes escénicas en Andalucía. La Feria de Palma viene exhibiendo cada edición una destacada selección de las mejores producciones de teatro, danza, circo, espectáculos para niños y niñas o teatro de calle de Andalucía del año. Durante estos años, la Feria de Palma del Río ha sido el gran referente de la defensa y puesta en valor de las artes escénicas andaluzas. Con el paso de los años se ha producido un lógico avance y una transformación constante del modelo de gestión y de ejecución del proyecto, acorde con la mayor profesionalización del sector.

short_description: Germans Boada is an industrial machinery & supplies company based in Rubí, Spain.
long_description: The origins of Germans Boada go back to 1950, when the Boada brothers invented a manual cutter for hydraulic mosaic work. More than sixty years later, with the second generation of founders on the management board, Germans Boada, S.A. has established itself as a leading company in the design, manufacturing and distribution of machinery and tools for cutting, laying and maintaining ceramic tiles. As a company that is internationally renowned for its dynamism and capacity for innovation, Germans Boada has had to keep evolving in order to cope with the growth it has experienced since it began, going through different stages and moving from the modest workshop where the Boada brothers made the first units by hand to new modern facilities. Germans Boada, S.A., RUBI was created in 1951 based on the invention of a manual cutter for hydraulic mosaic tiles. This new tool, which was given the name RUBI, served as the pillar for the development of a solid company that today designs, manufactures and distributes machinery and tools for cutting, installing and maintaining ceramic tiles.

long_description:
Die Greenlight-Consulting GmbH ist ein innovatives Beratungsunternehmen, das sich auf das Management von Projekten, sowie das Consulting in Service- und Supportprozessen spezialisiert hat. Innerhalb von Großunternehmen, dem Mittelstand sowie bei Staatlichen Einrichtungen unterstützen wir seit 2006 unsere Kunden mit einem breiten Spektrum an Know-how aus den Bereichen Finanz- und Rechnungswesen, Beschaffung, IT, HR, Controlling und Reporting sowie Real Estate. Einen messbaren Wert für Ihr Unternehmen schaffen wir mit Hilfe der erstklassigen Branchen- und Fachexpertise unserer Mitarbeiter, der Nähe zu Ihrem Unternehmen, sowie unserer großen Flexibilität, hoher Standards bei der professionellen Projektumsetzung und unseres hochqualifizierten Projektmanagements. Was uns auszeichnet, sind unsere motivierten Mitarbeiter. Durch erfolgreiche Teamarbeit, hohe Dienstleistungsqualität und Beachtung ethischer Werte im Umgang mit Kunden und Mitarbeitern erfüllen wir alle entscheidenden Faktoren, die eine erfolgreiche Zusammenarbeit ausmachen. Durch erfahrene Projektmanager und Business Consultants unterstützen wir in den Phasen Plan, Design, Build, Test und Deploy von Implementierungsprojekten. Perspektiven für die ZukunftGreenlight-Consulting steht für „Menschen, Werte und Leistung". Wir sind davon überzeugt, dass sich außergewöhnliche Ziele nur mit außergewöhnlichen Mitarbeitern umsetzen lassen, die bereit sind, jeden Tag ihr Bestes zu geben, sich weiterzuentwickeln und sich neuen Herausforderungen zu stellen. Dabei spielt unser zeitgemäßes Management, welches sich aus den Werten Offenheit, Fairness und Transparenz zusammensetzt, ebenfalls eine große Rolle. Nur die Kombination aus beidem, Menschen und Werten, führt zu unseren hochwertigen, innovativen und professionellen Consulting-Lösungen. Es sind diese Eckpfeiler, die unsere Greenlight-Vision jeden Tag ein Stück mehr Realität werden lassen: Mit Menschen, Werten und Leistung zu überzeugen. Das ist unsere Erfolgsphilosophie. Energy Healing is given by certified practitioners in hospitals and hospices to veterans as well as to many individuals who are seeking help. short_description: Ideal Agriculture is a fruit & vegetable market based in Küçükçekmece, Turkey.
long_description:
S. Zeki Birincioğlu's journey in the fresh fruit trade started with the import of bananas at the end of the 1980s, which expanded with the addition of kiwis to the portfolio. In those early years, Turkey experienced the kiwifruit for the first time and the brand "Verita" was born. By institutionalizing the Ideal Agricultural Product Trade, which was established in 2002, Birincioğlu has become a model fruit and vegetable supplier and distributor not only in Turkey but also across the world in a short period of time. Since 2002, Ideal has been working to introduce a variety of global tastes to Turkey and the world by providing high-quality services. Ideal has developed a service concept that employs every innovation and technology across all areas including fruit and vegetable cultivation, harvesting, standardization, storage, packaging, and logistics. For over five decades, Jim Marsh Auto Body Shop has proudly served the Las Vegas community with unwavering dedication and expertise. Since our humble beginnings in 1971, we have grown to become a cornerstone of the auto body industry, earning the trust and loyalty of countless customers. At Jim Marsh Auto Body Shop, our mission is simple yet powerful: to provide exceptional auto body service that goes beyond repairs. We strive to be more than just a repair shop; we aim to be your trusted partner in maintaining and restoring the beauty and functionality of your vehicle. At Jim Marsh Auto Body Shop, we envision a future where every customer who walks through our doors experiences the highest level of satisfaction and trust. We aim to be the go-to destination for auto body services in Las Vegas, renowned for our exceptional craftsmanship, cutting-edge techniques, and personalized approach. When you choose Jim Marsh Auto Body Shop, you're not just getting top-notch repairs; you're also getting personalized service from a team that genuinely cares.

short_description: L'ARTYRIE PARIS is a clothing store based in Paris, France.
long_description: L'Artyrie crée l'événement en mettant en avant une sélection de créateurs émergents talentueux dans les meilleurs emplacements de Paris. Prêt-à-porter, maroquinerie, accessoires : des marques contemporaines et premium sont ainsi sélectionnées pour participer aux pop-up store et salons. Ces événements permettent ainsi aux marques de présenter leurs collections physiquement à leurs clients, mais également de communiquer sur leurs actualités. C'est dans cette dynamique que L'Artyrie organise des boutiques éphémères sous forme de concept store multi-créateurs lors desquelles plusieurs marques exposent simultanément sur une période définie, allant de quelques jours à plusieurs mois. À chaque événement, l'Artyrie prévoit un vernissage permettant aux marques présentes de créer une synergie créative et commerciale autour de tous les acteurs de la mode avec qui nous sommes partenaires (journalistes, influenceurs, stylistes, photographes, concept store et bien d'autres). L'Artyrie organise ses événements dans des emplacements commerçants et prestigieux, essentiellement basés à Paris dans les quartiers du Marais, St-Honoré et St-Germain, drainant ainsi une clientèle autant quantitative que qualitative. Nous organisons également des pop-up store dans des emplacements stratégiques tels que des hôtels de luxe et galeries d'art .Ces lieux haut-de-gamme permettent ainsi de côtoyer une clientèle aisée de parisiens et de touristes en quête de marques haut-de-gamme que l'on ne trouve pas ailleurs.. short_description: Laboratório Filippin is a medical laboratory based in Ampére, Brazil.
long_description: Fundado em 8 de março de 1974 no município de Realeza/PR através de uma parceria entre o farmacêutico-bioquímico Dr. Olívio Domingos Filippin com o Hospital Imaculada Conceição, o Laboratório Filippin iniciou suas atividades prestando atendimentos aos pacientes internados no Hospital. Em 1991, em virtude de um crescente aumento do número de exames e a possibilidade de expansão, a empresa fundou sua sede própria, situada na Avenida Rubens César Caselani, Travessa 3. Em 1994, foi o primeiro laboratório da região sudoeste do Paraná a automatizar o setor da Bioquímica e Hematologia. Em 1998, o Laboratório adotou o atual nome fantasia, Laboratório Filippin, em virtude de que os próprios pacientes já chamavam assim o laboratório, que até então possuía o nome Imaculada Conceição, por ter sido fundado dentro do hospital Imaculada Conceição. Fernanda Branco Filippin é formada em farmácia pela Universidade Do Vale do Itajaí – UNIVALI e mestre em Farmácia-Toxicologia e análises toxicológicas pela Universidade de São Paulo – USP.

generated_description: Filippin Laboratory (Laboratório Filippin) is a clinical laboratory based in Santa Izabel do Oeste, Paraná, Brazil. Founded on March 8, 1974, by Dr. Olívio Domingos Filippin and the Hospital Imaculada Conceição, the laboratory initially provided services to inpatients. Over the years, it has expanded its services and technology, becoming the first in the southwest region of Paraná to automate its Biochemistry and Hematology sectors. In 1998, the laboratory joined the National Quality Control Program sponsored by the Brazilian Society of Clinical Analysis. In 2014, Msc. Fernanda Branco Filippin joined the laboratory, bringing new technologies and expertise. Laboratório Filippin has multiple units, including a first unit in Santa Izabel do Oeste and a second in Ampére, and is known for its commitment to quality and professional ethics.

long_description: Vous êtes une entreprise ou un particulier, notre food truck offre un service de qualité pour tous vos événements. Nous sommes fiers de proposer une cuisine savoureuse et personnalisée directement à nos clients. Derrière le Rout'art Gourmand, foodtruck bien installé dans le paysage Nantais, se cachent deux passionnés de cuisine : Hélène et Dominique. En nous rendant visite au camion, vous découvrirez une cuisine typée "street-food", saine et entièrement faite maison, gourmande et conviviale, servie à emporter dans des contenants respectueux de l'environnement. Du frais, du local, de la cuisine faite avec amour. Quand au burger c'est de l'excellence et de la gourmandise. Si vous voulez manger un burger fait maison c'est le food truck à connaître. Pain frais, tomates fraiches, cornichon frais, steak fraîchement moulé,frites fraiches même le ketchup est maison. Derrière ce joli nom aux consonances italiennes se cache encore aujourd'hui une activité d'épicerie fine basée essentiellement sur la noisette du Piémont, tenue par Hélène, et une charcuterie artisanale, gérée par Dominique.

long_description: MADERAS PORTU S.A Gracias al prestigio labrado durante más de 90 años de historia, Maderas Portu es el almacén de referencia en el suministro de productos y servicios del mundo de la madera. Avalados por nuestra experiencia, trabajamos permanentemente en la búsqueda de los mejores materiales y marcas del mercado. Esto nos posiciona como el almacén con mayor stock y variedad de oferta de nuestro ámbito, con una amplia cartera de clientes vinculados a los principales sectores productivos del territorio como carpinterías, empresas de construcción y reformas, de la industria ferroviaria, transporte, naval, etc. Además, nuestra clara vocación por la formación continua nos hace estar al día de las últimas novedades y ofrecer un asesoramiento experto a nuestros clientes. Nuestra amplia experiencia en el sector y nuestro constante foco en ofrecer siempre las últimas novedades nos permite desarrollar soluciones complejas y adaptadas a las necesidades específicas de nuestros clientes. long_description: In particular, we owe our thanks to Professor Paul Dieppe from the United Kingdom and Professor John Edmonds from Australia, both of whom have been and still are influential in the development of rheumatology in Malaysia. These meetings have been held annually since and are hosted by either society on alternate years. Since then, Singapore has hosted the "Workshops" in 1999, 2001, 2005 and 2009, while Malaysia hosted the "Workshops" in Penang in 2000 and 2004, Kuala Lumpur in 2002 and Petaling Jaya in 2008 and more recently in 2010. The year 1999 marked a special milestone for rheumatology in Malaysia as the first officially recognised tertiary rheumatology unit in the MOH was opened at Hospital Selayang, headed by Dr Azmillah Rosman. Other rheumatology training centres within the MOH are Hospital Tuanku Ja'afar Seremban and Hospital Putrajaya, whilst University Malaya Medical Centre and Hospital University Kebangsaan Malaysia serve as training centres for the academic institutions. This steady growth coupled with the increased confidence and maturity of its members, have allowed the birth of a new entity in the Arthritis Foundation of Malaysia (AFM) in 1994 – a patient-oriented foundation which complements the rheumatology service for patients in Malaysia.

short_description: Pack Elephant is a gift shop based in Grand Rapids, Michigan, United States.
long_description: The act of gift giving is often seen as a challenging chore that requires time, energy, and creativity that many people don't feel they have to invest. What should be a pleasurable gesture of kindness and appreciation often becomes an anxiety-filled obligation, defeating the whole purpose of giving. But there is now a resource that elevates the practice of gifting to an artform by making the process simple and easy. Pack Elephant is a black-owned/woman-owned and operated company dedicated to values-driven, socially conscious gifting. Through our vetted network of ethnically diverse artisans and makers, we offer a broad, diverse continuum of meaningful and curated gifts inspired by the varied aspects of life that people are most passionate about. Whether the desired theme be a particular social cause, BIPOC ownership, geography, or service to country (just to name a few), we help givers curate just the right personalized, custom gift for the person they wish to honor, and we do so with high touch customer service. The process is simple, but the outcome is profound. It's no accident that our company name and symbol are inspired by an animal of high emotional intelligence that thrives within a social structure that is both matriarchal and community-oriented. Pack Elephant empowers people to do good for many simply by doing good for one. A single Pack Elephant gift reflects the values of the giver, the receiver, and even the maker – all at the same time, and all done simply, personally, and elegantly.

short_description: Radio Grenlands is a radio network/station based in Porsgrunn, Norway.
long_description: Radio Grenland sender live over hele Grenland og Midt-Telemark hver eneste dag, og gir deg alt du trenger av lokale nyheter, sport, vær, trafikk og reportasjer i tillegg til favorittmusikken din på løpende bånd. Radio Grenland følger det som skjer i regionen, og med oss i øret holder du deg oppdatert på lokale nyheter, sport og kultur. Vårt kjerneområde er kommunene Porsgrunn, Skien, Siljan, Bamble, Notodden, Kragerø, Drangedal, Nome, Midt-Telemark, Hjartdal, Seljord og Nissedal og det bor i overkant av 130 000 mennesker i dette området. Musikk er viktig og vi spiller dagens største hits, blandet med de største og beste låtene fra 80-tallet og frem til i dag. Radio Grenland har en unik lytterposisjon i regionen, og er blant Norges mest populære radiostasjoner målt i oppslutning i eget dekningsområde. Vi gjør vårt beste for å fortjene tilliten hver eneste dag. Radio Grenland sender 24 timer i døgnet, 365 dager i året og du hører oss både på FM, DAB og på internett. Radio Grenland er deleid av og en del av Jærradiogruppen AS, som har blitt ett av Norges største lokalradiokonsern med eierinteresser i tradisjonsrike og populære radiostasjoner over hele landet.

long_description: Wir freuen uns über Ihr Interesse am Rehazentrum Schwerin. Seit 1997 bieten wir Rehabilitationsmaßnahmen in ambulanter Form an. Unser Hauptanliegen ist Ihre Wiedereingliederung in das berufliche und soziale Umfeld und die Sicherung Ihrer Behandlungserfolge in Ihrer gewohnten häuslichen und sozialen Umgebung. Am Standort Wuppertaler Straße kommen für diesen Zweck jährlich ca. 900 Patienten überwiegend nach orthopädischen oder chirurgischen Erkrankungen zu uns ins Haus. Neben den Leistungen der ambulanten Rehabilitation bieten wir Ihnen im Rehazentrum Schwerin in zwei Physiotherapiepraxen und in einer Praxis für Ergotherapie Behandlungen auf ärztliche Verordnung, um Ihre Genesung auch ohne Reha-Bedarf umfassend zu unterstützen. Selbstzahler und Betriebe finden aktive Bewegungsangebote unter therapeutischer Leitung, um den drohenden Folgen von Erkrankungen, Bewegungsmangel oder einseitigen Belastungen zu begegnen.2014 haben wir ein Zertifikat nach IQMP-Reha für eine hohe Versorgungsqualität erhalten. Das Konzept beinhaltet die Integration der Anforderungen von Patienten, Kostenträgern und Mitarbeitern an ein motivierendes Leistungsangebot und sorgt für Transparenz der Prozesse und Strukturen.

short_description: Relais & Châteaux Hotel Burg Schwarzenstein is a hotel based in Geisenheim, Germany.
long_description:
Inmitten der Weinberge, fernab vom Trubel des Alltags, thront das
Relais & Châteaux Hotel Burg Schwarzenstein hoch über dem Rheingau. Warme, elegante Farben, Tradition und Moderne raffiniert kombiniert,geschmackvolle Details wohin das Auge reicht sowie die privilegierte, ruhige Lagehoch über dem Rheingau, der aufmerksame, herzliche Service und nicht zuletztein strahlendes Lächeln – all dies macht Burg Schwarzenstein zu dem, was unsere
Gäste aus aller Welt so lieben – Ihr ganz persönliches Zuhause im Rheingau. Unsere 51 Zimmer und Suiten sind mit wertvollen Seidenstoffen und dunklem
Wengeholz gestaltet. Smarter Luxus und lässige Eleganz geben den Zimmern dasindividuelle Ambiente. Große bodentiefe Fenster und Türen lassen viel Licht in die
Räume und öffnen sie zu den vorgelagerten Loggien und Terrassen. Die purisitischen Badezimmer sind Wellness-Oasen, die mit Fußbodenheizung,Rainshowerduschen und edlen Clarians-Produkten ausgestattet wurden. Nelson Müller ist der Patron der Brasserie, die in den Pavillon mit dematemberaubenden Blick über die Weinberge gezogen ist. Der moderne und komplett verglaste Kubus mit den weitläufigen Terrassen trägtdie gleiche Handschrift, das Interieur wurde in Farbe und Design angepasst. Eine
Fruit de Mer Bar aus poliertem Marmor mit edlen Fischen, Schalentieren und
Austern ist der Blickfang der neuen Brasserie. Wände und Accessoires in edlen
Grün- und Petroltönen unterstreichen das lässige Flair. Ein Ambiente romantischer Eleganz bietet das Burgrestaurant, das sich direkt imhistorischen Burggebäude befindet. Rheingauer Lebensfreude und das Beste aus
Küche und Keller versprechen regionale Gaumenfreuden. Die Zutaten stammen fast ausschließlich von regionalen Erzeugern, die Rieslinge von befreundeten Winzern aus dem Rheingau. Ein absoluter Traum in der warmen Jahreszeit – die von Weinreben umrankte historische Burgterrasse.

The hotel offers 51 rooms and suites with a combination of warm and elegant colors, traditional and modern styles, and tasteful details. The rooms are designed with valuable fabrics and soft downholstery, providing a personalized ambiance with large floor-to-ceiling windows and doors that allow light into the rooms. The wellness-oriented bathrooms are equipped with floor heating, rain showers, and high-quality Clarians products. Nelson Müller is the Patron of the Brasserie, which is located in a pavilion with a stunning view of the vineyards. The restaurant, located in an historic castle building, offers a romantic and elegant ambiance, serving regional cuisine made with locally sourced ingredients from Rheingau-based producers.

locations: US, United States, California, Hamilton City, 95951, , , 39.7426598, -122.0135914
short_description: Réseau en Immigration Francophone Centre-Sud-Ouest de l'Ontario is an immigration attorney based in Hamilton City, California, United States.
long_description: Le Réseau Centre-Sud-Ouest est un Réseau de soutien à l'immigration francophone de la région Centre-Sud-Ouest de l'Ontario. Au Canada, il existe treize réseaux en immigration francophone (RIF) qui ont pour objectif de favoriser l'accueil, l'établissement et l'intégration réussie des immigrants francophones au sein des communautés francophones en situation minoritaire, un élément d'importance fondamentale au développement de ces dernières. Ces RIF sont les partenaires communautaires d'Immigration, Réfugiés, Citoyenneté Canada (IRCC) et représentent le mécanisme principal de concertation et de mobilisation en matière d'immigration francophone dans les communautés en situation minoritaire (CFSM) partout au Canada. Notre mission : Concerter, mobiliser, planifier et coordonner les acteurs de l'immigration francophone afin de FAVORISER, L'ATTRACTION, L'ACCUEIL, L'INTÉGRATION & L'ENRACINEMENT des nouveaux arrivants d'expression française dans les communautés francophones du Centre-Sud-Ouest de l'Ontario. Nos axes d'intervention Accroître le nombre d'immigrants d'expression française de manière à accroître le poids démographique des communautés francophones en situation minoritaire. Améliorer la capacité d'accueil des communautés francophones en situation minoritaire et renforcer les structures d'accueil et d'établissement pour les nouveaux arrivants d'expression française. Assurer l'intégration économique des immigrants d'expression française au sein de la société canadienne et des communautés francophones en situation minoritaire en particulier. Assurer l'intégration sociale et culturelle des immigrants d'expression française au sein de la société canadienne et communautés francophones en situation minoritaire

GHC has achieved ISO 9001 certification. ISO 9001 helps drive efficiency with the best standards of customer service at its heart. Our continually increasing portfolio of products and services can be of advantage to those customers wishing to reduce the number of suppliers they have to administer. We also provide an embroidery and printing service so you can add your company logo to our range of t-shirts, polos, sweatshirts, hoodies & hi-viz garments. When the inevitable happens and the impossible is called for, Safety Plus is the provider to take on the challenge. Whether you're an individual seeking a pair of safety work boots or a business outfitting your workforce with safety gear, Safety Plus have you covered. Based in Smethwick, Birmingham and established in 1988, we have a wealth of experience to help you find the correct products and services for you and your business.
